title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-5.21 - Definition of food processing establishment
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-5.21 - Definition of food processing establishment

State Regulations
A food processing establishment is a commercial establishment operated under license or permit of an appropriate regulatory authority where food is manufactured or packaged for human consumption at another establishment or place. Notes
